<h1 class="title__header">Common requests</h1>
</div><!-- title -->



<div class="container">

<div class="main">

<div class="content">

<p class="lead">We have duty to specify what information we publish, how it is available and whether it is free or if there is a charge. Here we have compiled the most common requests for information we recieve.</p>

<p>If you would like any of this information translated into a difference language, Braille or audio – or if you are unable to find the information you require on this page or the rest of the site – you can send a request to the FOI team. We also recommend using our search function as well if the information can't be found here.</p>

</div><!-- content -->

